videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson splits multiple defenders with a pocket pass to Austin Davis, who rises for the two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Simpson dimes Davis for Michigan dunk

videos.description: Michigan fans get into the Christmas spirit as The Grinch shoots jumpers during a timeout.
videos.headline: The Grinch gets buckets in Ann Arbor

videos.description: Charles Matthews snatches a rebound and goes coastal to lay in the deuce at the buzzer to give Michigan its first lead.
videos.headline: Michigan's Matthews beats buzzer with finger-roll
